Once you've done all that, you might want to add a user, remember adminknight.php? You renamed it, this is hard to explain but I'll try my best, say your domain you registerd was ScriptSales.freehostia.com, you need to visit scriptsales.freehostia.com/adminknight.php, for me I would need to visit scriptsales.freehostia.com/533jjss.php as I renamed my adminknight.php to 533jjss.php. Add a user with the username and password of your choice, and for the Auth, click Auth1 then Submit Query. Once you've done that, open SCAR. :) A basic auth example would be the following code, but please, this is just an exaple.

program Auth;

var
  gUser, gPass, gTempStr : string;

procedure Authenticate;
begin
  gUser := Readln('Auth username?');
  gPass := Readln('Auth password?');
  gTempStr := GetPage('http://www.YOURSITENAMEHERW.freehostia.com/?username=' + gUser + '&password=' + gPass + '&auth=AUTH1');
  if (gTempStr = 'ACCEPTED') then
   Writeln('Auth accepted')
  else begin
    Writeln('Error authenticating! Ending script.');
    TerminateScript;
  end;
end;

begin
  Authenticate;
end.
